{"tid":734330,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港之恥］疑似香港人大阪鬧市草叢痾尿（有圖）","createTime":"2018-07-08T14:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T00:15:19.000Z","uid":2023,"like":282,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"d214128dbe12e6a9beeeb59aa5b65243a205b74e","tid":734330,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"地點係難波大馬路，商店街對出<br />\n條友係我隔黎行得好急，之後無啦啦除褲對住草叢痾尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時後面幾十個人行過，但好似無咩人留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我即刻拍低，仲比佢發現我影緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢痾完，走去搵個fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢朋友應該都好撚羞恥，企到勁撚遠睇水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我影完就拿拿聲走左，驚比佢搶手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老老實實，我無聽到佢講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但從佢+佢朋友打扮，加上比人偷拍都成隻死狗咁，咁敢惡返轉頭，我都好肯定佢地係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/215817_8d587715c70a768d62aeb6a92a7ac794.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F215817_8d587715c70a768d62aeb6a92a7ac794.png&h=830e6079&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/215820_dc3897d59017aba3e693f010f65adb11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F215820_dc3897d59017aba3e693f010f65adb11.png&h=1490d372&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d5c2b30ddef11c1ad9bd45191594390121e9805","tid":734330,"uid":50712,"like":2,"dislike":49,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"火"},{"pid":"88a3b9db469fee833a41e15b6bc0e14f138a414a","tid":734330,"uid":89931,"like":7,"dislike":1,"scor